				<div class="param">
					<ul>
						<li>A widow in constant mourning for her deceased<br>husband who hopes to join him by having her life<br>taken by his murderer. To her, ongoing grief is<br>love—so as her love endures, she will never<br>change out of her mourning dress.</li>
