	<dl><dt
				>
				<span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/dcaa6a19b847a492e179bfe23fc6ec6d2.png"></span>
				<span>Sorrow's Requiem</span>
			</dt>
			<dd><div>If the user's HP is below 40% of max HP<br>when using this skill, increases the entire team's<br>defense by 30% for 15 seconds.<br>If the user's HP is above or equal to 40% of max HP,<br>reduces their HP to 30% of max HP and grants the<br>entire team a "Life Shield" that nullifies damage<br>relative to the amount of HP lost by the user<br>when using this skill.<br>This shield can stack with ordinary shields.</div></dd><dt
				>
