<div class="ability explanation">
	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/f9c2d9288412c72cf2277b7580c4fe5d2.png"></span><span>Mournful Heart II</span></dt><dd><div>Grants the user a unique force strike,<br>and increases force strike damage by 30%.<br>Their force strike dispels one buff from an enemy,<br>and restores 10% of the damage inflicted as HP<br>to the user. This recovery caps at 5% of their<br>maximum HP.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/350933fc3518d44a2f1ed162f7e191052.png"></span><span>Blindness Res +100%</span></dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to blindness by 100%.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/368330649dd4e9c07abc8582ae510ece2.png"></span><span>Healing Doublebuff IV</span></dt><dd><div>Grants an HP regen buff for 20 seconds each<br>time a defense up buff is received.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>
