			<div class="status">
				<div class="title">Adventurer Details</div>
				<div class="param">
					<ul>
						<li>With a new outfit, Alex has become Elisanne's<br>personal guard. The white hood represents her<br>leaving the assassin's life, and she swears a<br>vow upon her blade to safeguard her friend<br>and never lose heart, no matter what.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div></div><div class="skill explanation">
	<div class="title">Skills</div>
	<dl><dt
				>
				<span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/2a14e3aeaf8990581545b970f18bf5f82.png"></span>
				<span>Crisis Edge</span>
			</dt>
			<dd><div>Deals damage to the target, and reduces<br>their defense. After using this skill, or upon<br>using Umbral Erasure when the target has a<br>buff or is in break state, for a set period of<br>time it will be possible to trigger a "Skill Chain."<br>If Crisis Edge is activated during the<br>Skill Chain window, a variant with different<br>effects will be used instead, and it will deal<br>bonus damage if the attack connects.</div><div class="skill-detail">Damage: 202 × 3 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: 1,129<br>Special Effects:<br>・Defense -5%<br>　　Lasts 15 seconds<br>　　Does not stack<br><br><color=#00008B>During Skill Chain:</color><br>Damage: 202 × 3 hits<br>Damage: 485 × 1 hit<br>Skill Energy Required: 1,129<br>Damage Modifier:<br>・110% against enemies with reduced defense<br><br><color=#00008B>During Skill Chain + Enemy is Buffed:</color><br>Damage: 202 × 3 hits<br>Damage: 485 × 1 hit<br>Skill Energy Required: 1,129<br>Special Effects:<br>・Dispels Buffs<br>Damage Modifier:<br>・104% against enemies with reduced defense<br><br><color=#00008B>During Skill Chain + Enemy is in Break State:</color><br>Damage: 235 × 3 hits<br>Damage: 658 × 1 hit<br>Skill Energy Required: 1,129<br>Damage Modifier:<br>・150% against enemies in break state<br></div></dd><dt
				>
				<span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/18bb75cee57f186afb031e6ca02c56f92.png"></span>
				<span>Umbral Erasure</span>
			</dt>
			<dd><div>Deals damage to the target, and inflicts<br>poison. After using this skill, or upon<br>using Crisis Edge when the target has a<br>buff or is in break state, for a set period of<br>time it will be possible to trigger a "Skill Chain."<br>If Umbral Erasure is activated during the<br>Skill Chain window, a variant with different<br>effects will be used instead, and it will deal<br>bonus damage if the attack connects.</div><div class="skill-detail">Damage: 553 × 1 hit<br>Skill Energy Required: 1,129<br>Special Effects:<br>・Poison<br>　　Lasts 15 seconds<br>　　Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>　　Damage: 58.2<br><br><color=#00008B>During Skill Chain:</color><br>Damage: 553 × 1 hit<br>Damage: 442 × 1 hit<br>Skill Energy Required: 1,129<br>Damage Modifier:<br>・110% against poisoned enemies<br><br><color=#00008B>During Skill Chain + Enemy is Buffed:</color><br>Damage: 553 × 1 hit<br>Damage: 442 × 1 hit<br>Skill Energy Required: 1,129<br>Special Effects:<br>・Dispels Buffs<br>Damage Modifier:<br>・104% against poisoned enemies<br><br><color=#00008B>During Skill Chain + Enemy is in Break State:</color><br>Damage: 648 × 2 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: 1,129<br>Damage Modifier:<br>・150% against enemies in break state<br></div></dd></dl></div>
