<div class="ability explanation">
	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/a2241ae1de30904a24117f1388bd71782.png"></span><span>Reduced Defense Punisher +30%</span></dt><dd><div>Increases damage to enemies with reduced<br>defense by 30%.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/bd7de81c28d0b9c93b0edbfc86b0cb6a2.png"></span><span>Guardian Shadow II</span></dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to blindness<br>and paralysis by 100%.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/d3edea4a52a651ab75575f278704b8a82.png"></span><span>Poisoned Punisher +30%</span></dt><dd><div>Increases damage to poisoned enemies by 30%.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>・The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities and represent the adventurers at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unlocked, not the stats when first obtained.</div><div>・Some skills have different effects when used as a shared skill.</div><div>・Adventurers with the same name cannot be put into the same team.</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. For more information about summoning, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab.</div><div>2. Alberian Battle Royale skins for the adventurers featured in this summon showcase will go on sale and will cost fewer items to unlock. Note that some adventurers do not have adventurer skins.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1665640800,update_time1648636527